\c 24
\s UPawuli eyisibotshwa umangalelwa kuFelike eKesariya
\p
\v 1 Kwathi emva kwensuku ezinhlanu\x + 21.18,27. 23.11.\x* uAnaniya\x + 23.2. 23.30,35.\x* umpristi omkhulu wehla labadala lomkhulumeli othile uTertulo\x + 25.6,7. 25.1.\x*, abamangalela uPawuli kumbusi\x + 24.10. Mat. 27.2.\x*.
\v 2 Kwathi esebiziwe, uTertulo waqala uku\add m\add*cala esithi: Ukuthula okukhulu sikuzuzile ngawe, lemisebenzi emihle yenzakele kulesisizwe ngokunakekela kwakho,
\v 3 ngazo zonke indlela lakuzo zonke indawo siyakwemukela\x + Luka 8.40.\x*, mhlekazi Felike\x + Luka 1.3.\x*, ngakho konke ukubonga.
\v 4 Kodwa ukuze ngingakubambeleli kakhulu, ngiyakuncenga ukuthi ngomusa wakho\x + 2 Kor. 10.1.\x* usizwe ngokufitshane.
\v 5 Ngoba lindoda siyifice iyinkathazo, njalo ingeyenza umvukela phakathi kwamaJuda wonke\x + 17.6.\x* emhlabeni jikelele\x + Mat. 24.14.\x*, lomkhokheliqembu wobubhazuka bamaNazaretha\x + 24.5. 28.22.\x*;
\v 6 eyake yazama lokungcolisa ithempeli\x + 21.28.\x*; esike sayibamba sithanda ukuyehlulela ngokomlayo wethu\x + Joha. 18.31.\x*,
\v 7 kodwa kwafika uLisiya induna enkulu wa\add m\add*thatha ngodlakela olukhulu ezandleni zethu\x + 21.32,33. 23.27.\x*,
\v 8 elaya abamangaleli bakhe ukuthi beze kuwe\x + 23.30.\x*; ongathi, ngoku\add m\add*buzisisa wena uqobo, ungaba lakho ukwazi kuye ngazo zonke izinto thina esimmangalela ngazo.
\v 9 LamaJuda lawo avuma, esithi lezizinto zinjalo\x + 4.9.\x*.
\p
\v 10 UPawuli wasephendula, umbusi esemqhwebile ukuthi akhulume\x + 24.10. Mat. 27.2.\x*, \add wathi\add*: Ngoba ngiyazi ukuthi sekuyiminyaka eminengi ungumahluleli phezu kwalesisizwe, ngiyaziphendulela ngesibindi esikhulu ngezinto zami\x + 19.33.\x*,
\v 11 njengoba ungakubona ukuthi kaku\add ka\add*dluli insuku ezilitshumi lambili\x + 21.18,27. 24.1.\x*, lokhu ngenyukele eJerusalema\x + 21.4,12,15.\x* ukukhuleka\x + 8.27.\x*;
\v 12 njalo kabangificanga ethempelini\x + 25.8. 28.17.\x* ngiphikisana lomuntu loba ngivusa isiphithiphithi exukwini, loba emasinagogeni, loba emzini.
\v 13 Futhi bangeke baqinise ngezinto abangimangalela ngazo khathesi\x + 17.17.\x*.
\v 14 Kodwa ngiyavuma kuwe lokhu, ukuthi ngendlela abayibiza ngokuthi\x + 9.2.\x* yibubhazuka\x + 24.5. 28.22.\x*, ngokunjalo ngiyamkhonza uNkulunkulu wabobaba\x + 2 Tim. 1.3. Seb. 27.23.\x*, ngikholwa konke okulotshiweyo emlayweni lakubaprofethi\x + 26.22. 28.23. Roma 3.21.\x*;
\v 15 ngilethemba kuNkulunkulu\x + 24.21. 23.6.\x*, abalilindeleyo labo uqobo lwabo, elokuthi kuzakuba khona ukuvuka kwabafileyo\x + 24.21. 23.6.\x*, okwabalungileyo kanye labangalunganga\x + Dan. 12.2.\x*.
\v 16 Njalo kulokho mina ngiyazama, ukuthi ngibe lesazela\x + 23.1. Jobe 27.6.\x* esingelacala phambi kukaNkulunkulu labantu isikhathi sonke\x + 1 Kor. 10.32. Fil. 1.10.\x*.
\v 17 Kwathi emva\x + Mat. 26.61.\x* kweminyaka eminengi ngafika\x + 18.22,23. 19.8,10. 20.31.\x* ukuletha izipho zomusa esizweni sakithi leminikelo\x + Roma 15.25-28. 1 Kor. 16.1,3. 2 Kor. 8.4. 9.1,12. Seb. 11.29. Gal. 2.10.\x*;
\v 18 ngikulezizinto\x + Luka 12.1. Seb. 26.12.\x* amaJuda athile\x + 21.26,27. 26.21.\x* avela eAsiya angifica ethempelini ngihlanjululwe, kungekho ixuku loba isiphithiphithi\x + 2.9.\x*;
\v 19 afanele ukuba khona lapha phambi kwakho a\add ngi\add*cale uba elolutho ngami\x + 23.30. 25.16.\x*;
\v 20 kumbe bona ngokwabo kabatsho, ukuthi baficani okungalunganga kimi, mhla ngimi phambi komphakathi\x + 22.30.\x*,
\v 21 ngaphandle kwalelolizwi elilodwa, engalimemeza ngimi phakathi kwabo \add ngisithi\add*: Ngokuvuka kwabafileyo mina ngiyehlulelwa yini lamuhla\x + 23.6.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Kwathi uFelike wabadlulisela phambili, esezwile lezizinto esazi ngokupheleleyo\x + 23.15.\x* izinto ngaleyondlela\x + 9.2.\x*, esithi: Nxa uLisiya induna enkulu isiyehlile\x + 24.7.\x*, ngizayihlolisisa indaba yenu\x + 25.21.\x*;
\v 23 waselaya induna yekhulu ukuthi agcinwe uPawuli, lokuthi abe lenkululeko\x + 28.16. 27.3.\x*, njalo kungalelwa muntu wakibo uku\add m\add*ncedisa kumbe ukuza kuye\x + 4.23. 1 Tim. 5.8. Joha. 1.11.\x*.
\s UPawuli utshumayela kuFelike ngoKristu
\p
\v 24 Kwathi emva kwensuku ezithile, uFelike weza loDrusila umkakhe engumJudakazi, wathumela ukubiza uPawuli, wamuzwa mayelana lokholo kuKristu.
\v 25 Kwathi esakhuluma ngokulunga langokuzithiba\x + Gal. 5.23. 2 Pet. 1.6.\x* langokwahlulela okuzayo\x + 17.31.\x*, uFelike watshaywa luvalo waphendula \add wathi\add*: Hamba okwakhathesi; nxa sengizuze ithuba elihle ngizakubizela kimi\x + 17.32. Isa. 55.6.\x*;
\v 26 njalo ngesikhathi esifananayo wayethemba futhi ukuthi uzanikwa imali nguPawuli, ukuze amkhulule\x + 24.17.\x*; ngakho wayehlezi embizela kuye ekhuluma laye.
\v 27 Kodwa sekugcwaliseke iminyaka emibili, uFelike wemukela omlandelayo uPorkiyu uFestusi; uFelike efisa ukuthokozisa amaJuda wamtshiya uPawuli ebotshiwe\x + 25.9. 12.3.\x*.